function tagHumanoid(humanoid, player) if humanoid ~= nil and player ~= nil then local creatorTag = Instance.new("ObjectValue") creatorTag.Name = "creator" creatorTag.Value = player creatorTag.Parent = humanoid debris:AddItem(creatorTag, 1) end end
function getMassOfObject(obj) local children local mass = 0 if type(obj) == "userdata" then children = obj:GetChildren() elseif type(obj) == "table" then children = obj end if children then for i = 1, #children do if children[i]:IsA("BasePart") then mass = mass + children[i]:GetMass() end if #children[i]:GetChildren() > 1 then mass = mass + getMassOfObject(children[i]) end end end return mass end
function flapWings() local lWeld local rWeld local sign = 1 local count = 0
local initLC1 local initRC1
if BirdClone then lWeld = BirdClone:FindFirstChild("LeftWingWeld") rWeld = BirdClone:FindFirstChild("RightWingWeld") if lWeld and rWeld then initLC1 = lWeld.C1 initRC1 = rWeld.C1 while BirdClone.Parent and lWeld and rWeld do lWeld.C1 = lWeld.C1 * CFrame.Angles(0, 0, -sign * math.pi/30) rWeld.C1 = rWeld.C1 * CFrame.Angles(0, 0, sign * math.pi/30) count = count + 1 if count > 6 then sign = sign * -1 count = count%6 end wait(0.1) end end end end
function follow() local stopped = false local bv if BirdClone then bv = BirdClone:FindFirstChild("FollowBV") end while BirdClone and Bird and myTorso and bv do local distance = (myTorso.Position - BirdClone.Position).magnitude if distance > 5.0 then stopped = false if BirdClone then BirdClone.CFrame = CFrame.new(BirdClone.Position, myTorso.Position + Vector3.new(0, BirdClone.Position.Y - myTorso.Position.Y, 0)) if BirdClone then bv.Parent = BirdClone end if distance > 8.0 then bv.velocity = (myTorso.Position - BirdClone.Position).unit * 20.0 + Vector3.new(0, 2, 0) else bv.velocity = (myTorso.Position - BirdClone.Position).unit * 20.0 * (distance/24) + Vector3.new(0, 2, 0) end end else if not stopped then stopped = true bv.velocity = Vector3.new(0, 0, 0) BirdClone.Velocity = Vector3.new(0, 0, 0) bv.Parent = nil end end wait() end if Bird then Bird.Parent = nil end if BirdClone then BirdClone:Destroy() end Handle.Transparency = 0 end

Mouse_Icon = "rbxasset://textures/GunCursor.png" Reloading_Icon = "rbxasset://textures/GunWaitCursor.png"
Tool = script.Parent
Mouse = nil
function UpdateIcon() if Mouse then Mouse.Icon = Tool.Enabled and Mouse_Icon or Reloading_Icon end end
function OnEquipped(ToolMouse) Mouse = ToolMouse UpdateIcon() end
function OnChanged(Property) if Property == "Enabled" then UpdateIcon() end end
Tool.Equipped:connect(OnEquipped) Tool.Changed:connect(OnChanged)
